<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.1">
<l>pōtalarnta poḻilcōlaip puṟameṅkum porutiraikaḷ</l>
<l>tātutira vantalaikkum taṭamaṇṇit teṉkaraimēl</l>
<l>mātavaṉṟā ṉuṟaiyumiṭam vayalnāṅkai varivaṇṭu</l>
<l>tēteṉaveṉ ṟicaipāṭun tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where Mādhava dwells on the southern shore</l>
<l rend="indent">of the wide Maṇṇi [River]</l>
<l>Where dashing waves come crashing, so pollen falls on all sides</l>
<l>Of the garden groves where buds blossom, is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai</l>
<l>In Nāṅkai with fields where striped bees sing melodies saying, “tētu.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
